Patti Name Meaning in English

What does the name Patti mean? What is the meaning of the name Patti, lucky number, lucky stone, origin and religion.

Patti or Pattie is a feminine given name, and a surname. As a given name, it can be a short form or diminutive of Patricia, meaning 'noblewoman'.

Patti Name Meaning, Origin & Details

Meaning: Patrician of noble birth Details: Short form of Patricia, the feminine form of Patrick, from the Latin patricius, meaning "nobleman" or "patrician". Gender: Girl Origin: English Religion: Christian Suitable for: Girls / Female / Women Hardness: Easy to pronounce, Patti is a short name Uniqueness: It is a common name Short & Easy: Yes Syllables: 5 Letters and 1 Words
